
The numberâ€¯2026 is the first entry of a new layer of the spiral.  
In that layer the outer radius is \(r=23\).  

The eight neighbour positions of \((23,-22)\) are  

\[
\begin{aligned}
(22,-23) &\text{: }2208,\\
(22,-22) &\text{: }2025,\\
(22,-21) &\text{: }1850,\\
(23,-23) &\text{: }2209,\\
(23,-21) &\text{: }2027,\\
(24,-23) &\text{: }2210,\\
(24,-22) &\text{: }2211,\\
(24,-21) &\text{: }2212 .
\end{aligned}
\]

Adding them gives  

\[
\begin{aligned}
\sum & = 2025+2027+2209+1850+2210+2211+2212+2208\\
&= 16952 .
\end{aligned}
\]

\[
\boxed{16952}
\]
